quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  96,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  96,1,parho ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) apne Rab ke naam ke sath jis ne peda kya
  96,2,jamay hue khoon ke aik Lothray insaan ki takhleeq ki
  96,3,"parho, aur tumhara Rab bara kareem hai"
  96,4,jis ne qalam ke zareya se ilm sikhaya
  96,5,ensaan ko woh ilm diya jisay woh nah jaanta tha
  96,6,"hargiz nahi, ensaan sar kashi karta hai"
  96,7,iss bana par ke woh apne aap ko be niaz daikhta hai
  96,8,palatna yaqeenan tairay Rab hi ki taraf hai
  96,9,tum ne dekha uss shakhs ko
  96,10,jo aik bande ko mana karta hai jabkay woh namaz parhta ho ?
  96,11,tumhara kya khayaal hai agar ( woh bandah ) raah raast par ho
  96,12,ya parhaiz gari ki Talqeen karta ho ?
  96,13,tumhara kya khayaal hai agar ( yeh mana karne wala shakhs haq ko ) jhutlata aur mun morta ho ?
  96,14,kya woh nahi jaanta ke Allah dekh raha hai ?
  96,15,"hargiz nahi, agar woh baz nah aaya to hum is ki peshani ke baal pakar kar usay khinchin ge"
  96,16,uss peshani ko jo jhooti aur sakht khata car hai
  96,17,woh bulaa le apne hamion ki touli ko
  96,18,hum bhi azaab ke firshton ko bulaa len ge
  96,19,"hargiz nahi, uss ki baat nah manu aur sajda karo aur ( apne Rab ka ) qurb haasil karo"
